---
title: Asparagus & Mushroom Truffle Pizzas with Prosciutto, Burrata & Arugula Salad
description: Springtime is here and we’re pouncing on the short and sweet asparagus season! And what better way to parade the farm-fresh flavor of these prized green stalks than on thin-crust pizzas? You'll make them from scratch with refrigerated pizza dough and a duo of luxe cheeses: mozzarella and its rich, cream-filled cousin, burrata. Truffle cream sauce and sautéed creminis offer rich, earthy aromas, while red grapes sweeten a peppery arugula side salad. All in all, it’s a lavish meal that’ll have you sprung for spring!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/62324442b6f6fa03f608246e-ef9f887d.jpg
